com.analog.lyric.dimple.solvers.optimizedupdate

Class CostEstimationTableWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.analog.lyric.dimple.solvers.optimizedupdate.CostEstimationTableWrapper

  • @Internal
public final class CostEstimationTableWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Similar to the TableWrapper class, but for the purpose of estimating the cost of employing the optimized update algorithm. Instead of storing a factor table's data, this implementation only stores information about its dimensions and its density.

    0.07
